INSTALLATION
    Safira can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions. Please also have a look at the file "REQUIREMENTS" for
    information on the tools required to run, compile, and develop Safira.


DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of Safira. It can also be
    downloaded at <http://service-technology.org/files/safira/safira.pdf>.
